Class OrderOutcome

java.lang.Object
ca.yorku.cmg.lob.core.OrderOutcome
public class OrderOutcome extends Object
Captures the outcome of an order processing operation HalfBook.processOrder(IOrder, int) An arraylist of Trade objects keeps the resulting trades while a IOrder implementing object captures the unfulfilled order (which my have zero quantity, i.e., the order was fully fulfilled).
